BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:34JFJSHxhu3ctDSsWOkaN
SUMMARY:Sturtevant Ravine Work Party!
DTSTAMP:20260306T004520Z
DTSTART:20260307T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Sturtevant Ravine. \\nH
