SUMMARY:Seattle: Hitt's Hill
DTSTAMP:20260306T004520Z
DTSTART:20260307T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Hitt’s Hill Park . \\nJ
	oin EarthCorps and Green Seattle Partnership to restore Hitt’s Hill! Event
	s consist mostly of removing non-native species (like ivy and blackberry) 
	and preparing areas for our winter planting events. No experience necessar
	y! \\nPlease note: We are no longer able to provide port-o-potties (portab
	le bathrooms) to events at this location. Please visit Rainier Playfield\\
	\, 3700 S Alaska St\\\, Seattle\\\, WA 98118 for a restroom\\\, or a local
	 grocery store\\\, like PCC. \\nThe Basics \\nRegistration is required. Ea
	rthCorps supplies gloves\\\, tools\\\, water and snack bars. We will teach
	 you everything you need to know! No experience necessary\\\, just come re
	ady to learn something new! Be sure to sign in at registration when you ar
	rive. \\nRegister to meet.\n\nhttps://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event
	/seattle-hitts-hill/\n\nFrom The Seattle Parks Foundation
