DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Frink Park. \\nWe’re go
	ing to visit violence upon some invasive species today in preparation to r
	eplace them with native local species this fall. You can expect to be pull
	ing out mostly ivy and holly. This site has been under restoration since 2
	022 so it’s a good place to see what’s been done and what your work area w
	ill look like a couple of years from now. \\nRegister\n\nhttps://www.seatt
	leparksfoundation.org/event/frink-ridge-invasive-plants-removal-2/\n\nFrom
	 The Seattle Parks Foundation
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/frink-ridge-invasive-plant
	s-removal-2/
